INSTALL
=======

Requirements
s3cmd (http://s3tools.org/s3cmd)
python setuptools

CENTOS / RHEL
--------------
yum install python-setuptools
wget https://github.com/s3tools/s3cmd/archive/master.zip
unzip master.zip
python s3cmd-master/setup.py install
mkdir /root/hypersrv.com/plesk-to-s3/
cp {plesk-to-s3,daily,monthly}.sh /root/hypersrv.com/plesk-to-s3/
chmod 700 {plesk-to-s3,daily,monthly}.sh /root/hypersrv.com/plesk-to-s3/

# Add the jobs to root cron

crontab -e

# enter below

0 1 * * * /root/hypersrv.com/plesk-to-s3/daily.sh > /dev/null 2>&1
0 1 1 * * /root/hypersrv.com/plesk-to-s3/monthly.sh > /dev/null 2>&1

# Configure monthly.sh and daily.sh with correct parameters

